{"tid":359304,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴：曼聯霸氣回歸","createTime":"2017-08-14T11:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T18:03:48.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3870fbc503f989510a45a63ef1db486958fed08b","tid":359304,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/7b/d8/manchester-united_2nwae9nnfgzo1jzunqk5y433u.jpg?t=-563914299&amp;w=620&amp;h=430\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2F7b%2Fd8%2Fmanchester-united_2nwae9nnfgzo1jzunqk5y433u.jpg%3Ft%3D-563914299%26w%3D620%26h%3D430&h=259d94a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曼聯在英超新季首輪比賽4：0大炒韋斯咸，摩連奴指球隊霸氣回歸，現時信心十足。<br />\n<br />\n今場英超曼聯鬥韋斯咸，盧卡古梅開二度 ，加上安東尼馬迪爾及保羅普巴各自建功，幫助曼聯4：0大勝對手。<br />\n<br />\n在費格遜離開之後，曼聯的進攻火力一直為人批評，今場比賽盧卡古、拉舒福特及馬迪爾踢起來完全令比歷的韋斯咸難以招架，難怪摩連奴賽後大表滿意。<br />\n<br />\n「其實這場比賽不易踢，領先2：0時對手曾有機會入球，我不相信這是一場簡單的4：0比賽。然後我們入第3球，可以放鬆一點了。我們不算是踢得最好，但球員表現很高質素，很高興大家踢來信心十足。」摩連奴說。<br />\n<br />\n他又大讚高身價轉會的盧卡古踢得出色：「盧卡古首場入球非常美妙，無論是朗尼、莫拉達、拿卡錫迪也好，能夠在首場入球是最完美的事。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=XgYSpDQkWPfYcZ3%2BIBN8pF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=dd9e06ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"9acad8bd923ff50a9b316e3671bff5188797bb04","tid":359304,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:31:11.000Z","msg":"皇者曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c58362512dafd479e0e683ec8abbe69100973e","tid":359304,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:36:04.000Z","msg":"想知霸氣英文係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8197be1901c179e71185440d4c9f5792dfe4015b","tid":359304,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T11:38:24.000Z","msg":"Nigga football<img src=\"/asset